		I'm passionate about performance optimization, developer experience, and
		building tools that make complex systems more accessible. Whether it's
		modularizing a TypeScript/C++/WASM codebase, designing compiler
		infrastructure, or mentoring engineers, I thrive on technical challenges
		that have real impact.
